        <h2 >Email Marketing - Build An Email List</h2>
        <p>
            Email marketing is a marketing strategy where you collect emails in order to send out offers, up-to-date information, and current news about what's going on with you and your business in bulk. Email marketing is an effective strategy for reaching out to customers directly because email is still one of the most widely used form of communication still today.The tricky part about email marketing is actually getting the emails in the first place. To get an email list started you should probably start by asking the customers you already have. Onces you've reached your limit there you can move on to a more streamlined approach of collecting email addresses. This leads me to my next poing, offering free resources on your website in exchange for an email address. 
        </p>
